faqs.question: Can I join your team?
faqs.answer:
# Joining Neoneko

[info]We're always open to welcoming new talented team members![/info]

## How to Apply:
1. Join our [link]https://discord.neoneko.xyz|Discord server[/link]
2. Message Yusarina directly about your interest

[note]We evaluate each application carefully to ensure a good fit for both the team and the applicant.[/note]
